愛國愛黨.得到應有的下場."},{"pid":"921ee8a966c885d4cb4d8d6e51fa6fa001a5caea","tid":810681,"uid":185953,"like":10,"dislike":0,"score":10,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-08T07:59:07.000Z","msg":"信中國的下場<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"43edd98acb0b18dcdbf9aef5b74e3270cb762de7","tid":810681,"uid":59898,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-08T08:02:07.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ae01a1660c0f32746b75d219ce2f1cdd26fa5685","tid":810681,"uid":65406,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-08T08:03:30.000Z","msg":"感謝黨。黨既恩情"},{"pid":"1994170d9e0f8059907e51b726ae1883b68c997d","tid":810681,"uid":177590,"like":19,"dislike":1,"score":18,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-08T08:03:48.000Z","msg":"吊頸都要著supreme<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n下次supreme 出返條吊頸繩啦"},{"pid":"7f7a55c581bed12a2be4711ce1f59cd32756f86c","tid":810681,"uid":20867,"like":6,"dislike":1,"score":5,"quote":{"pid":"47d454bfd73e02d4c3268953ee8f978bf4554941","tid":810681,"uid":79563,"like":16,"dislike":1,"score":15,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-08T07:25:44.000Z","msg":"支那所謂「金融科技」, 人唔笑, 狗都吠<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-08T08:07:37.000Z","msg":"中國人自己都知道<br />\n連衣食住行都有問題/危機<br />\n竟然仲有人會去信<br />\n本質系偷呃拐騙既金融<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d730381890010bfe45f16fc8f6b5bdb829f82509","tid":810681,"uid":38523,"like":38,"dislike":1,"score":37,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-08T08:09:12.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">福氣來</span></span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">住屋住到生癌真係世界首創<br />\n搵幾多隻奶波魔魔上踩港都冇用<br />\n</span></span><br />\n奶波魔魔家屬示意圖<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/09/08/103744_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F09%2F08%2F103744_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg&h=45c1f1e4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"><br />\n［有線中國組］內地租盤甲醛超標 租戶入住兩月患白血病 三日後身亡</span></span><br />\n<br />\n國內最大長租公寓營運商自如早前被指推高北京房租後，再陷入甲醛超標的風波。<br />\n<br />\n一名阿里巴巴員工5月初搬入自如在杭州出租的房間，兩個月後確診患上白血病，接著在短短三日後去世。妻子到他生前住所進行空氣檢測，發現屋內多處甲醛濃度超標，懷疑同死因有關。<br />\n<br />\n消息一出，紛紛有自如租戶在自己單位進行測試，發現甲醛超標不是個別例子；更有受甲醛超標影響的自如租戶退租後，發現自如將有問題單位再出租。<br />\n<br />\n自如一方面發聲明強調所有裝修材料和家具等都符合國家標準，但又同時在全國收回所有首次出租的租盤。他們表示會在百分百檢測合格後，才重新出租；亦會向6月1日後，入住首次出租盤的租戶提供空氣檢測服務。若證實有超標問題，可無條件退租和換租。<br />\n<br />\n本身隸屬鏈家集團的自如靠著收樓、裝修再轉租出去的盈利模式，迅速發展起來。到了今時今日，業務遍布包括北上廣深在內的九個城市，擁有超70萬個租盤，租戶達160萬人。<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"><br />\n你以為死左就有得安樂？<br />\n推火葬強挖棺材燒屍！<br />\n生為國人 何其有幸</span></span><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/09/08/132238_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F09%2F08%2F132238_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg&h=3a85dc47&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">福氣來</span></span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">🙏🙏🙏🙏🙏🙏🙏🙏🙏🙏🙏🙏</span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">生為國人 何其有幸 🙏<br />\n生為國人 何其有幸 🙏<br />\n生為國人 何其有幸 🙏<br />\n生為國人 何其有幸 🙏<br />\n生為國人 何其有幸 🙏<br />\n生為國人 何其有幸 🙏<br />\n生為國人 何其有幸 🙏<br />\n生為國人 何其有幸 🙏</span></span>"},{"pid":"19d7041c4e69a6a374d8a9ee34ff868f38fd15a0","tid":810681,"uid":62815,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-08T08:11:43.000Z","msg":"愛國教育又贏<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"830976295ed30b5b958f41b350aa7fc2b0b8dd18","tid":810681,"uid":191926,"like":0,"dislike":5,"score":-5,"quote":{"